REMARKS: 
<bibRefCitation id="845B4B47FF9BFFFD5914FCCEFE4C6227" author="Rondani, C." box="[266,511,834,862]" pageId="86" pageNumber="87" pagination="243 - 274" refId="ref370928" refString="Rondani, C. (1875 a) Species italicae ordinis dipterorum (Muscaria Rndn.) collectae et observatae. Stirps XXII Lonchaeinae Rndn. Bullettino della Societa Entomologica Italiana, 6 (4) [1874], 243 - 274." type="journal article" year="1875">Rondani (1875a: 266)</bibRefCitation>
described 
<taxonomicName id="27CA4D35FF9BFFFD5A69FCCEFCDA6224" authorityName="Rondani" authorityYear="1875" box="[631,873,835,861]" class="Insecta" family="Chamaemyiidae" genus="Leucopis" kingdom="Animalia" order="Diptera" pageId="86" pageNumber="87" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="palliditarsis">
<emphasis id="D2BEEAA4FF9BFFFD5A69FCCEFCDA6224" box="[631,873,835,861]" italics="true" pageId="86" pageNumber="87">Leucopis palliditarsis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
without specifying either the 
<taxonomicName id="27CA4D35FF9BFFFD5CA9FCCEFABE6224" box="[1207,1293,835,861]" family="Number" pageId="86" pageNumber="26" rank="family">number</taxonomicName>
or the sex of the specimens. Günter Morge labeled the specimen in the MZUF as the 
<typeStatus id="3F718814FF9BFFFD5BF0FCEAFBE362F8" box="[1006,1104,871,897]" pageId="86" pageNumber="87">holotype</typeStatus>
but, as far as we know, never indicated this specimen as the 
<typeStatus id="3F718814FF9BFFFD5A38FC06FD3B62DC" box="[550,648,907,933]" pageId="86" pageNumber="87">holotype</typeStatus>
in any of his publications on 
<taxonomicName id="27CA4D35FF9BFFFD5BFFFC06FB2462DC" authorityName="Hendel" authorityYear="1910" box="[993,1175,907,933]" class="Insecta" family="Chamaemyiidae" kingdom="Animalia" order="Diptera" pageId="86" pageNumber="87" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="family">Chamaemyiidae</taxonomicName>
(
<bibRefCitation id="845B4B47FF9BFFFD5CB6FC06FAF762DC" author="Morge, G." box="[1192,1348,906,933]" pageId="86" pageNumber="87" pagination="909 - 945" refId="ref360243" refString="Morge, G. (1959 a) Monographie der palaearktischen Lonchaeidae (Diptera). Beitrage zur Entomologie, 9 (1 - 2), 1 - 92, 323 - 371, 909 - 945." type="journal article" year="1959">Morge 1959a</bibRefCitation>
, 
<bibRefCitation id="845B4B47FF9BFFFD5D4FFC06FA2B62DC" author="Morge, G." box="[1361,1432,907,933]" pageId="86" pageNumber="87" pagination="381 - 434" refId="ref360313" refString="Morge, G. (1962 a) Monographie del palaearktischen Lonchaeidae. Beitrage zur Entomologie, 12 (3 - 4), 381 - 434." type="journal article" year="1962">1962a</bibRefCitation>
, 
<bibRefCitation id="845B4B47FF9BFFFD58D9FC22FEBD62B3" author="Morge, G." box="[199,270,943,970]" pageId="86" pageNumber="87" pagination="434 - 437" refId="ref360341" refString="Morge, G. (1962 b) Kopulationsapparat und Legrohr der Typen von Leucopis aphidiperda Rondani, 1847 und Leucopis aphidivora Rondani, 1847 (Diptera: Chamaemyiidae). Beitrage zur Entomologie, 12 (3 - 4), 434 - 437." type="journal article" year="1962">1962b</bibRefCitation>
) and therefore did not publish a 
<typeStatus id="3F718814FF9BFFFD5A93FC22FD4762B0" box="[653,756,943,969]" pageId="86" pageNumber="87">lectotype</typeStatus>
designation (I.C.Z.N. 1999: Article 74.5). 
<bibRefCitation id="845B4B47FF9BFFFD5CFDFC22FEF86294" author="Raspi, A. &amp; Benelli, G." pageId="86" pageNumber="87" pagination="199 - 219" refId="ref365136" refString="Raspi, A. &amp; Benelli, G. (2016) On the identity of Leucopis (Diptera Chamaemyiidae) described by Camillo Rondani: a revision of eight silver fly species. Bulletin of Insectology, 69 (2), 199 - 219." type="journal article" year="2016">Raspi &amp; Benelli (2016: 209)</bibRefCitation>
designated a 
<typeStatus id="3F718814FF9BFFFD59FAFC5EFDF86294" box="[484,587,979,1005]" pageId="86" pageNumber="87">lectotype</typeStatus>
(
<specimenCount id="F6CCFD3FFF9BFFFD5A43FC5EFDC36294" box="[605,624,979,1005]" pageId="86" pageNumber="87" type="female">♀</specimenCount>
